quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  20,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  20,1,taah
  20,2,hum ne yeh quran tum par is liye nazil nahi kya hai ke tum museebat mein par jao
  20,3,yeh to aik yaad dehani hai har is shakhs ke liye jo daray
  20,4,nazil kya gaya hai uss zaat ki taraf se jis ne peda kya hai zameen ko aur buland asmano ko
  20,5,woh Rehman ( kaayenaat ke ) takhat saltanat par jalva farma hai
  20,6,maalik hai unn sab cheezon ka jo asmano aur zameen mein hain aur jo zameen o aasman ke darmain mein hain aur jo matti ke neechay hain
  20,7,"tum chahay apni baat pukaar kar kaho, woh to chupkay se kahi hui baat balkay is se makhfi tar baat bhi jaanta hai"
  20,8,"woh Allah hai, is ke siwa koi khuda nahi, is ke liye behtareen naam hain"
  20,9,aur tumhe kuch moose ki khabar bhi pohanchi hai ?
  20,10,"jab ke is ne aik aag dekhi aur apne ghar walon se kaha ke"" zara tehro, mein ne aik aag dekhi hai, shayad ke tumahray liye aik aadh angara le aon, ya iss aag par mujhe ( rastay ke mutaliq ) koi rahnumai mil jaye """
  20,11,"wahan pouncha to puraka gaya"" ae moose !"
  20,12,"mein hi tera rab hon, jotiyan utaar day to waadi muqaddas tawee mein hai"
  20,13,"aur mein ne tujh ko chuun liya hai, sun jo kuch wahi kya jata hai"
  20,14,"mein hi Allah hon, mere siwa koi khuda nahi hai, pas to meri bandagi kar aur meri yaad ke liye namaz qaim kar"
  20,15,"qayamat ki gharri zaroor anay wali hai mein uss ka waqt makhfi rakhna chahta hon, taakay har mutnaqas apni sae ke mutabiq badla paye"
  20,16,"pas koi aisa shakhs jo uss par imaan nahi lata aur apni khwahish nafs ka bandah ban gaya hai tujh ko uss gharri ki fikar se nah rok day, warna to halakat mein par jaye ga"
  20,17,"aur ae moose, yeh tairay haath mein kya hai? """
  20,18,"moose ne jawab diya"" yeh meri laathi hai, is par take laga kar chalta hon, is se apni bakrion ke liye pattay جھاڑتا hon, aur bhi bohat se kaam hain jo is se laita hon """
  20,19,"farmaya"" pheink day is ko moose """
  20,20,is ne pheink diya aur yakayak woh aik saanp thi jo daud raha tha
  20,21,"farmaya"" pakar le is ko aur dar nahi, hum usay phir waisa hi kar den ge jaisi yeh thi"
  20,22,"aur zara apna haath apni baghal mein daba, chamakta howa niklay ga baghair kisi takleef ke yeh doosri nishani hai"
  20,23,is liye ke hum tujhe apni barri nishanain dikhaane walay hain
  20,24,"ab to firaon ke paas ja, woh sarkash ho gaya hai """
  20,25,"moose ne arz kya"" parvar-digaar, mera seenah khol day"
  20,26,aur mere kaam ko mere liye aasaan kar day
  20,27,aur meri zabaan ki girah Suljha day
  20,28,taakay log meri baat samajh saken
  20,29,aur mere liye mere apne knbe se aik wazeer muqarrar kar day
  20,30,"haroon, jo mera bhai hai"
  20,31,uss ke zareya se mera haath Mazboot kar
  20,32,aur is ko mere kaam mein shareek kar day
  20,33,taakay hum khoob teri paki bayan karen
  20,34,aur khoob tera charcha karen
  20,35,"to hamesha hamaray haal par nigran raha hai """
  20,36,"farmaya"" diya gaya jo to ne manga ae moose"
  20,37,hum ne phir aik martaba tujh par ahsaan kya
  20,38,yaad kar woh waqt jabkay hum ne teri maa ko ishara kya aisa ishara jo wahi ke zareya se hi kya jata hai
  20,39,ke is bachay ko sandooq mein rakh day aur sandooq ko darya mein chore day darya usay saahil par pheink day ga aur usay mera dushman aur is bachay ka dushman utha le ga mein ne apni taraf se tujh par mohabbat taari kar di aur aisa intizam kya ke to meri nigrani mein paala jaye
  20,40,"yaad kar jabkay teri behan chal rahi thi, phir ja kar kehti hai,"" mein tumhe uss ka pata dun jo iss bachay ki parwarish achi terhan kere ?"" is terhan hum ne tujhe phir teri maa ke paas pouncha diya taakay uss ki aankhh thandhi rahay aur woh ranjida nah ho aur ( yeh bhi yaad kar ke ) to neshakhs ko qatal kar diya tha, hum ne tujhe iss phandey se nikala aur tujhe mukhtalif aazmayshon se guzaraa aur to mudin ke logon mein kayi saaltehra raha phir ab theek apne waqt par to aa gaya hai ae moose"
  20,41,mein ne tujh ko apne kaam ka bana liya hai
  20,42,"ja, too aur tera bhai meri nshanyon ke sath a war dekho, tum meri yaad mein taqseer nah karna"
  20,43,jao tum dono firaon ke paas ke woh sarkash ho gaya hai
  20,44,"is se narmi ke sath baat karna, shayad ke woh nasiyaat qubool kere ya dar jaye """
  20,45,"dono ne arz kya"" parvar-digaar, hamein andesha hai ke woh hum par zayad-ti kere ga ya pal parre ga """
  20,46,"farmaya"" daro mat, mein tumahray sath hon, sab kuch sun raha hon aur dekh raha hon"
  20,47,"jao is ke paas aur kaho ke hum tairay rab ke firistaday hain, bani Israel ko hamaray sath jaane ke liye chore day aur un ko takleef nah day hum tairay paas tairay rab ki nishani le kar aeye hain aur salamti hai uss ke liye jo raah e raast ki pairwi kere"
  20,48,"hum ko wahi se bataya gaya hai ke azaab hai uss ke liye jojhutla-ay aur mun moray """
  20,49,"firaon ne kaha"" acha, to phir tum dono ka rab kon hai ae moose? """
  20,50,"moose ne jawab diya"" hamara rab woh hai jis ne har cheez ko uss ki saakht bakhsh, phir is ko rasta bataya """
  20,51,"firaon bola"" aur pehlay jo naslen guzar chuki hain un ki phir kya haalat thi? """
  20,52,"moose ne kaha"" uss ka ilm mere rab ke paas aik noshte mein mehfooz hai mera rab nah chokta hai nah Bhoolta hai """
  20,53,"wohi jis ne tumahray liye zameen ka farsh bichhaya, aur uss mein tumahray chalne ko rastay banaye, aur oopar se pani barsaya, phir uss ke zareya se mukhtalif aqsam ki pedawar nikaali"
  20,54,khao aur apne janwaron ko bhi churao yaqeenan iss mein bohat si nishanain hain aqal rakhnay walon ke liye
  20,55,"isi zameen se hum ne tum ko peda kya hai, isi mein hum tumhe wapas le jayen ge aur isi se tum ko dobarah nikalen ge"
  20,56,hum ne firaon ko apni sab hi nishanain deikhein magar wohjhutla-ay chala gaya aur nah maana
  20,57,"kehnay laga"" ae moose, kya to hamaray paas is liye aaya hai ke apne jaadoo ke zor se hum ko hamaray malik se nikaal bahar kere ?"
  20,58,"acha, hum bhi tairay muqablay mein waisa h jaadoo laatay hain tey kar le kab aur kahan muqaabla karna hai nah hum iss qarardad se phrin ge nah to phiryo (phirna) khuُle maidan mein samnay aa ja """
  20,59,"moose ne kaha"" jashan ka din tey howa, a war din charrhey log jama hon """
  20,60,firaon ne palat kar apne saaray hthknde jama kiye aur muqablay mein aa gaya
  20,61,"moose ne ( ain mauqa par giroh maqabil ko mukhatib kar ke ) kaha"" shamat ke maro, nah Jhooti tohmatain bandho Allah par, warna woh aik sakht azaab se tumhara satyanaas kar day ga jhoot jis ne bhi ghara woh namuraad howa """
  20,62,yeh sun kar unn ke darmain ikhtilaaf raye ho gaya aur woh chupkay chupkay baahum mahswara karne lagey
  20,63,"aakhir-kaar kuch logo n ne kaha ke"" yeh dono to mehez jadugar hain inn ka maqsad yeh hai ke apne jaadoo ke zor se tum ko tumhari zameen se be dakhal kar den aur tumahray misali tareeq zindagi ka khtama kar den"
  20,64,"apni saari tadbeerye aaj ikathe kar lau aur Aika kar ke maidan mein آؤبس yeh samajh lau ke aaj jo ghalib raha wohi jeet gaya """
  20,65,"jadugar bolay"" moose, tum phenkhte ho ya pehlay hum phinkin? """
  20,66,"moose ne kaha"" nahi, tum hi phenko"" yakayak unn ki rasiyaan aur unn ki lathyan unn ke jaadoo ke zor se moose ko daurti hui mehsoos honay lagen"
  20,67,aur moose apne dil mein dar gaya
  20,68,"hum ne kaha"" mat dar, to hi ghalib rahay ga"
  20,69,"pheink jo kuch tairay haath mein hai, abhi inn ki saari banawati cheezon ko niglay jata hai yeh jo kuch bana kar laaye hain yeh to jadugar ka fraib hai, aur jadugar kabhi kamyaab nahi ho sakta, khuwa kisi shaan se woh aeye """
  20,70,"aakhir ko yahi howa ke saaray jadugar sjday mein gira diye gay aur pukaar utthay"" maan liya hum ne haroon aur moose ke rab ko """
  20,71,"firaon ne kaha"" tum imaan le aeye qabal is ke ke mein tumhe is ki ijazat deta? maloom ho gaya ke yeh tumhara guru hai jis ne tumhe jadoo gari sikhayi thi acha, ab mein tumahray haath paon mukhalif simtao se katwataا hon aur khajoor ke tnon par tum ko suli deta hon phir tumhe pata chal jaye ga ke hum dono mein se kis ka azaab ziyada sakht aur der pa hai"" ( yani mein tumhe ziyada sakht saza day sakta hon ya moose )"
  20,72,"jadogaron ne jawab diya"" qasam hai uss zaat ki jis ne hamein peda kya hai, yeh hargiz nahi ho sakta ke hum roshan nishanain samnay aa jaane ke baad bhi ( sadaqat par ) tujhe tarjeeh den, too jo kuch karna chahay kar le to ziyada se ziyada bas isi duniya ki zindagi ka faisla kar sakta hai"
  20,73,"hum to apne rab par imaan le aeye taakay woh hamari khataien maaf kar day aur is jadoo gari se, jis par to ne hamein majaboor kya tha, dar guzar farmaiye Allah hi acha hai aur wohi baqi rehne wala hai """
  20,74,haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo mujrim ban kar apne rab ke huzoor haazir hoga uss ke liye jahannum hai jis mein woh nah jie ga nah marey ga
  20,75,"aur jo is ke huzoor momin ki hesiyat se haazir ho ga, jis ne naik amal kiye hon ge, aisay sab logon ke liye buland darjay hain"
  20,76,"sada bahhar baagh hain jin ke neechay nhrin beh rahi hon gi, un mein woh hamesha rahen ge yeh jaza hai uss shakhs ki jo pakizgee ikhtiyar kere"
  20,77,"hum ne moose par wahi ki ke ab raton raat mere bundon ko le kar chal par, aur unn ke liye samandar mein se SOOKHI sarrak bana le, tujhe kisi ke taqub ka zara khauf nah ho aur nah ( samandar ke beech se guzarte hue ) dar lagey"
  20,78,peechay se firaon apne lashkar le kar pouncha aur phir samandar unn par chhaa gaya jaissa ke chhaa jaane ka haq tha
  20,79,"firaon ne apni qoum ko gumraah hi kya tha, koi sahih rahnumai nahi ki thi"
  20,80,"ae bani Israel , hum ne tum ko tumahray dushman se nijaat di, aur tor ke dayen janib tumhari haazri ke liye waqt muqarrar kya aur tum par mann o salwa utaara"
  20,81,"khao hamara diya howa pak rizaq aur usay kha kar sar kashi nah karo, warna tum par mera ghazab toot parre ga aur jis par mera ghazab toota woh phir gir kar hi raha"
  20,82,"Albata jo tauba kar le aur imaan laaye aur naik amal kere, phir seedha chalta rahay, uss ke liye mein bohat dar guzar karne wala hon"
  20,83,aur kya cheez tumhe apni qoum se pehlay le aayi moose ?
  20,84,"uss ne arz kya"" woh bas mere peechay aa hi rahay hain mein jaldi kar ke tairay huzoor aa gaya hon ae mere rab, taakay to mujh se khush ho jaye """
  20,85,"farmaya"" acha, to suno, hum ne tumahray peechay tumhari qoum ko azmaish mein daal diya aur samri ne inhen gumraah kar dala """
  20,86,"moose sakht ghsse aur ranj ki haalat mein apni qoum ki taraf palta ja kar uss ne kaha"" ae meri qoum ke logo, kya tumahray rab ne tum se achay waday nahi kiye thay? kya tumhe din lag gay hain? ya tum apne rab ka ghazab hi apne oopar lana chahtay thay ke tum ne mujh se wada khalaqi ki? """
  20,87,"unhon ne jawab diya"" hum ne aap se wada khalaqi kuch apne ikhtiyar se nahi ki, maamla yeh howa ke logon ke zyorat ke boojh se hum ld gay thay aur hum ne bas unn ko pheink diya tha"" phir is terhan samri ne bhi kuch dala"
  20,88,"aur un ke liye aik bichhre ki mourat bana kar nikaal laya jis mein se bail ki si aawaz nikalti thi log pukaar utthay"" yahi hai tumhara khuda aur moose ka khuda, moose usay bhool gaya """
  20,89,kya woh nah dekhte thay ke nah woh unn ki baat ka jawab deta hai aur nah un ke naffa o nuqsaan ka kuch ikhtiyar rakhta hai ?
  20,90,"haroon ( moose ke anay se ) pehlay hi un se keh chuka tha ke"" logo, tum iss ki wajah se ftne mein par gay ho, tumhara rab to rehman hai, pas tum meri pairwi karo aur meri baat manu """
  20,91,"magar onhon ne is se keh diya ke"" hum to isi ki parastish karte rahen ge jab taq ke moose wapas nah aa jaye """
  20,92,"moose ( qoum ko dantnay ke baad haroon ki taraf palta aur ) bola"" haroon, tum ne jab dekha tha ke yeh gumraah ho rahay hain"
  20,93,"to kis cheez ne tumhara haath pakra tha ke mere tareeqay par amal nah karo? kya tum ne mere hukum ki khilaaf warzi ki? """
  20,94,"haroon ne jawab diya"" ae meri maa ke betay, meri daarhi nah pakar, nah mere sir ke baal khech, mujhe iss baat ka dar tha ke to aa kar kahe ga tum ne bani Israel mein phoot daal di aur meri baat ka paas nah kya """
  20,95,"moose ne kaha"" aur samri, tera kya maamla hai? """
  20,96,"is ne jawab diya"" mein ne woh cheez dekhi jo inn logon ko nazar nah aayi, pas mein ne rasool ke naqsh qadam se aik muthi utha li aur uss ko daal diya mere nafs ne mujhe kuch aisa hi sujhaya"""
  20,97,"moose ne kaha"" acha to ja, ab zindagi bhar tujhe yahi pkarte rehna hai ke mujhe nah chouna aur tairay liye bazprs ka aik waqt muqarrar hai jo tujh se hargiz nah talle ga aur dekh apne iss khuda ko jis par to rehjahowa tha, ab hum usay jala dalain ge aur rezah rezah kar ke darya mein baha den ge"
  20,98,"logo, tumhara khuda to bas aik hi Allah hai jis ke siwa koi aur khuda nahi hai, har cheez par uss ka ilm haawi hai """
  20,99,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, a seen terhan hum pichlle guzray hue halaat ki khabrain tum ko sanatay hain, aur hum ne khaas apne haan se tum ko aik"" zikar"" ( drsِ nasiyaat ) ataa kya hai"
  20,100,jo koi iss se mun moray ga woh qayamat ke din sakht baar gunah uthaye ga
  20,101,"aur aisay sab log hamesha is ke wabaal mein girftar rahen ge, aur qayamat ke din unn ke liye ( iss jurm ki zimma daari ka boojh ) bara takleef da boojh hoga"
  20,102,uss din jabkay soor phuuNkaa jaye ga aur hum mujrimon ko iss haal mein ghair layein ge ke un ki ankhen ( dehshat ke maaray ) pathrayi hui hon gi
  20,103,aapas mein chupkay chupkay kahin ge ke duniya mein mushkil hi se tum ne koi das din guzaray hon ge
  20,104,"hamein khoob maloom hai ke woh kya baatein kar rahay hon ge ( hum yeh bhi jantay hain ke ) uss waqt un mein se jo ziyada se ziyada mohtaat andaza laganay wala hoga woh kahe ga ke nahi, tumhari duniya ki zindagi bas aik din ki thi"
  20,105,yeh log tum se poochtay hain ke aakhir uss din yeh pahar kahan chalay jayen ge? kaho ke mera rab un ko dhool bana kar ura day ga
  20,106,aur zameen ko aisa hamwar chtil maidan bana day ga
  20,107,ke is mein tum koi bil aur sillouette nah dekho ge
  20,108,"is roz sab log munaadi ki pukaar par seedhay chalay ayen ge, koi zara akarr nah dikha sakay ga aur aawazian Rehman ke agay dab jayen gi, aik sarsarahat ke siwa tum kuch nah suno ge"
  20,109,"uss roz Shafaat kargar nah ho gi, ila yeh ke kisi ko Rehman is ki ijazat day aur is ki baat sunna pasand kere"
  20,110,woh logon ka agla pichla sab haal jaanta hai aur doosron ko is ka poora ilm nahi hai
  20,111,logon ke sir uss HAYUU o Qayyum ke agay jhuk jayen ge namuraad hoga jo uss waqt kisi zulm ka baar gunah uthaye hue ho
  20,112,aur kisi zulm ya haq talfi ka khatrah nah hoga uss shakhs ko jo naik amal kere aur iss ke sath woh momin bhi ho
  20,113,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, isi terhan hum ne isay quran arabi bana kar nazil kya hai aur is mein terhan terhan se tnbihat ki hain shayad ke yeh log kaj rawi se bachchen ya un mein kuch hosh ke assaar iss ki badolat peda hon"
  20,114,"pas baala o bartar hai Allah , Padasha haqeeqi aur dekho, quran parhnay mein jaldi nah kya karo jab taq ke tumhari taraf uss ki wahi takmeel ko nah poanch jaye, aur dua karo ke ae parvar-digaar mujhe mazeed ilm ataa kar"
  20,115,"hum ne iss se pehlay aadam ko aik hukum diya tha, magar woh bhool gaya aur hum ne uss mein azm nah paaya"
  20,116,"yaad karo woh waqt jabkay hum ne firshton se kaha tha ke aadam ko sajda karo woh sab to sajda kar gay, magar aik iblees tha ke inkaar kar betha"
  20,117,"is par hum ne aadam se kaha ke"" dekho, yeh tumhara aur tumhari biwi ka dushman hai, aisa nah ho ke yeh tumhe jannat se nikalwa day aur tum museebat mein par jao"
  20,118,yahan to tumhe yeh asaishen haasil hain ke nah bhukay nangay rehtay ho
  20,119,"nah pyaas aur dhoop tumhe satati hai """
  20,120,"lekin shetan ne is ko phslaya kehnay laga"" aadam, batau tumhe woh darakht jis se abdi zindagi aur la zawaal saltanat haasil hoti hai? """
  20,121,aakhir kaar woh dono ( miyan biwi ) uss darakht ka phal kha gay nateeja yeh howa ke foran hi un ke sattar aik dosray ke agay khul gay aur lagey dono apne aap ko jannat ke patoon se dhanknay aadam ne apne rab ki nafarmani ki aur raah e raast se bhatak gaya
  20,122,phir uss ke rab ne ussay bargzida kya aur is ki tauba qubool kar li aur usay hadaayat bakhsh
  20,123,"aur farmaya"" tum dono ( fareeq, yani ensaan aur shetan ) yahan se utar jao tum aik doosray ke dushman raho ge ab agar meri taraf se tumhe koi hadaayat puhanche to jo koi meri uss hadaayat ki pairwi kere ga woh nah bhatkay ga nah bad bakhti mein mubtala ho ga"
  20,124,"aur jo mere"" zِkr"" ( drsِ nasiyaat ) se mun moray ga uss ke liye duniya mein tang zindagi ho gi aur qayamat ke roz hum usay andha athayin ge """
  20,125,"woh kahe ga"" parvar-digaar, duniya mein to mein aankhon wala tha, yahan mujhe andha kyun aُthaya? """
  20,126,"Allah taala farmaiye ga"" haan, isi terhan to hamari ayaat ko, jabkay woh tairay paas aayi theen, too ne bhula diya tha usi terhan aaj to bhulaya ja raha hai """
  20,127,"iss terhan hum hadd se guzarnay walay aur apne rab ki ayaat nah maan-ne walay ko ( duniya mein ) badla dete hain, aur akhirat ka azaab ziyada sakht aur ziyada der pa hai"
  20,128,phir kya inn logon ko ( tareekh ke is sabaq se ) koi hadaayat nah mili ke inn se pehlay kitni hi qomon ko hum halaak kar chuke hain jin ki ( barbaad shuda ) bustiyon mein aaj yeh chaltay phirtay hain? Dur haqeeqat iss mein bohat si nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo aqal Saleem rakhnay walay hain
  20,129,agar tairay rab ki taraf se pehlay aik baat tey nah kar di gayi hoti aur mohlat ki aik mddt muqarrar nah ki ja chuki hoti to zaroor inn ka bhi faisla chuka diya jata
  20,130,"pas ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jo baatein yeh log banatay hain unn par sabr karo, aur apne rab ki hamd o Sana ke sath uss ki tasbeeh karo Sooraj niklny se pehlay aur ghuroob honay se pehlay, aur raat ke auqaat mein bhi tasbeeh karo aur din ke kinaroon par bhi, shayad ke tum raazi ho jao"
  20,131,"aur nigah uttha kar bhi nah dekho dunewi zindagi ki uss shaan o Shaukat ko jo hum ne inn mein se mukhtalif qisam ke logon ko day rakhi hai woh to hum ne inhen azmaish mein daalnay ke liye di hai, aur tairay rab ka diya howa rizaq"
  20,132,"apne ahal o Ayal ko namaz ki Talqeen karo aur khud bhi is ke paband raho hum tum se koi rizaq nahi chahtay, rizaq to hum hi tumhe day rahay hain aur injaam ki bhalai taqwa hi ke liye hai"
  20,133,woh kehte hain ke yeh shakhs apne rab ki taraf se koi nishani ( moujza ) kyun nahi lata? aur kya un ke paas aglay shifon ki tamam talemaat ka bayan wazeh nahi aa gaya ?
  20,134,"agar hum uss ke anay se pehlay inn ko kisi azaab se halaak kar dete to phir yahi log kehte ke ae hamaray parvar-digaar, to ne hamaray paas koi rasool kyun nah bheja ke zaleel o ruswa honay se pehlay hi hum teri ayaat ki pairwi ikhtiyar kar letay"
  20,135,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho, har aik injaam car ke intzaar mein hai, pas ab muntazir raho, anqareeb tumhe maloom ho jaye ga ke kon seedhi raah chalne walay hain aur kon hadaayat Yafta hain"
